      • dateAndTime

        public java.util.Calendar dateAndTime
        Calendar object with date and time information, when the Transponder was read If a Reader has no support for date information, then only the time information is valid.
        Thus, the isTimerValid and isDateValid flags should be evaluated before the use of the Calendar oblect.
